data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the highly sought-after Continental Reserve community! This exceptional property offers an array of features that will captivate any prospective buyer. Wake up every morning to views of Sombrero Peak right from your own backyard. With no rear neighbor, you'll enjoy unparalleled privacy and serenity in this tranquil oasis. Step inside and be greeted by the elegance of tile throughout the home, providing a seamless flow and easy maintenance. Say goodbye to carpet headaches! The great room off the kitchen is the heart of the home, providing an open and inviting space for gatherings and entertaining. It's the perfect layout to host family and friends while staying connected. This home boasts a generous-sized bonus room, perfect for a home office, playroom, or entertainment area. The possibilities are endless, and it's sure to accommodate your unique needs. Retreat to the spacious primary suite, designed with your comfort in mind. Relaxation awaits you in this private sanctuary, offering ample space and a soothing atmosphere. The updated travertine bathrooms add a touch of luxury to your everyday routine. Immerse yourself in a spa-like experience every time you step into these beautifully designed spaces. Situated on a peaceful cul-de-sac and backing to a common area, this home ensures a peaceful and quiet environment. It's the ideal setting for creating lasting memories with loved ones. Escape the Arizona heat in your very own pebble tec pool, where you can take a refreshing dip or simply lounge by the water's edge. Additionally, the built-in BBQ allows for outdoor culinary adventures, creating the perfect setting for summer barbecues and evening relaxation. Ask about the TEP Residential GO SOLAR Home Program. Very few homeowners are accepted into this program and it is fully transferable with a FIXED monthly TEP bill of $252. NO SOLAR PANELS on home, NO LEASE or LOAN
